DTSTAMP:20260416T234317Z
SUMMARY:Contact Baystate: Landry
DESCRIPTION:• emailed [2026-04-09 Thu]\n• "a co-I with expertise in chronic
  airway disease"\n• "accessibility to clinical specimens"\n• "needs to col
 laborate with an airway cell biologist"\n• "lack of an expert in CF sputum
